# Download

## Installer

The easiest way to download Sculpin is to use the installer. This will install the latest development
version of Sculpin in the directory in which this command is executed.

    curl -s http://getsculpin.com/install | php

Want a specific release? **Pro Tip: There are no releases. Yet.**

    curl -s http://getsculpin.com/install | php -- --release=1.0.0

Once installed, using Sculpin is easy!

    php sculpin.phar list
    php sculpin.phar init
    php sculpin.phar generate


## Source

Sculpin can also be downloaded from GitHub. Clone or fork
[https://github.com/sculpin/sculpin](https://github.com/sculpin/sculpin).

The source installation of Sculpin operates a little differently.
See the [README](https://github.com/sculpin/sculpin/blob/master/README.md)
for instructions on using the development version of Sculpin.


